## Detailed Component Breakdown

### 1. Historical Period Generation
```mermaid
graph LR
    A[Period N] --> B[Entropy Engine]
    B --> C[Events + Mutations]
    C --> D[LLM Context]
    D --> E[HistoricalPeriodResponse]
    E --> F[Narrative]
    E --> G[Structures]
    E --> H[Events]
    
    F --> I[Next Period Context]
    G --> J[Structure Collection]
    H --> I
```

### 2. Structure Placement Algorithm
```mermaid
graph TD
    A[Structures with<br/>Relative Positions] --> B[Calculate Target Position]
    B --> C{Direction}
    C -->|north| D[y -= distance]
    C -->|south| E[y += distance]
    C -->|east| F[x += distance]
    C -->|west| G[x -= distance]
    C -->|diagonal| H[x,y adjust]
    
    D --> I[Check Overlaps]
    E --> I
    F --> I
    G --> I
    H --> I
    
    I --> J{Position Free?}
    J -->|Yes| K[Place Structure]
    J -->|No| L[Spiral Search]
    L --> I
    
    K --> M[Add to Occupied List]
```

### 3. Road Generation Flow
```mermaid
graph TD
    A[Structures] --> B[Sort by Significance]
    B --> C[For Each High-Sig Structure]
    C --> D[Find Nearest Structures]
    D --> E[Calculate Distance]
    E --> F{Distance < Max?}
    F -->|No| C
    F -->|Yes| G[Generate Path]
    
    G --> H[Linear Interpolation]
    H --> I[Apply Noise Curvature]
    I --> J[Add Waypoints]
    J --> K{Long Road?}
    K -->|Yes| L[Add Waystations]
    K -->|No| M[Road Complete]
    L --> M
    
    M --> N{More Structures?}
    N -->|Yes| C
    N -->|No| O[All Roads Generated]
```

### 4. Terrain Collapse Process
```mermaid
graph TD
    A[Structures + Roads] --> B[Create Influence Map]
    
    B --> C[Structure Influences]
    B --> D[Road Influences]
    
    C --> E[Radius = f(size)]
    C --> F[Elevation = f(type)]
    C --> G[Strength = significance]
    
    D --> H[Width = f(quality)]
    D --> I[Flatten = true]
    
    E --> J[Influence List]
    F --> J
    G --> J
    H --> J
    I --> J
    
    J --> K[During Chunk Generation]
    K --> L[Calculate Base Elevation]
    L --> M[Apply Influences]
    M --> N{Near Structure?}
    N -->|Yes| O[Blend to Target Elevation]
    N -->|No| P{On Road?}
    P -->|Yes| Q[Flatten Terrain]
    P -->|No| R[Use Base Elevation]
    
    O --> S[Modified Elevation]
    Q --> S
    R --> S
```

## Streaming Events Timeline

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Node as World Generation Node
    participant Entropy as Entropy Engine
    participant LLM
    participant Placer as Structure Placer
    participant Roads as Road Generator
    participant Collapse as Collapse Function
    
    Client->>Node: Start World Generation
    
    alt History Enabled
        Node->>Client: history_generation_start
        Node->>Entropy: Generate Period 0
        Entropy->>LLM: Request narrative
        LLM-->>Node: Period 0 data
        
        Node->>Entropy: Generate Period 1
        Entropy->>LLM: Request narrative (with context)
        LLM-->>Node: Period 1 data
        
        Note over Node: ... More periods ...
        
        Node->>Client: history_generation_complete
        
        Node->>Placer: Place structures
        Placer-->>Node: Coordinates assigned
        Node->>Client: structure_placement_complete
        
        Node->>Roads: Generate roads
        Roads-->>Node: Roads created
        Node->>Client: road_generation_complete
        
        Node->>Collapse: Create influence map
        Collapse-->>Node: Collapse data ready
        Node->>Client: terrain_collapse_complete
    end
    
    Node->>LLM: Generate world description
    LLM-->>Client: world_gen_chunk (stream)
    LLM-->>Client: world_gen_chunk (stream)
    LLM-->>Client: world_gen_chunk (stream)
    
    Node->>Client: World Generation Complete
```

